-> Added spring-boot-started-web, jackson-databind, jaxb-api dependencies to pom.xml file.

-> Created class Webconfig in package com.example.bookapi.config which implements WebMvcConfigurer. It is used to setup content negotiation in my application.

-> Content Negotitation allow the controllers of the application to handle different media type using Accept headers.

